title: The Mars Volta - Nissan Live Sets DVD
description:
Ok guys, this is a much better version of the previous DVD I made for this show.
If you have already downloaded the other one and don&#039;t feel like you need this one, don&#039;t feel like you have to have this, but if you like menus and other flashy stuff, here you are. One major bonus is that all of the intros and outros that were present on the last DVD are now gone (except for the first intro on miranda, I left that one as an introduction.) 

Created with Nero Vision using videos posted on thecomatorium.com/forum by nfscoy.
